OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRoyal Mail asks to stop    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSaturday letter deliveries 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Royal Mail has asked the government if 
OL,6, it can stop its letter deliveries on   
OL,7, Saturdays, as it seeks to turn its     
OL,8, fortunes around after slumping to a    
OL,9, loss in the first half of the year.    
OL,11,FThe business said it wanted to move    
OL,12,Ffrom a six-days-a-week letter delivery 
OL,13,Fto five, from Monday to Friday only.   
OL,15,FHowever, parcel services would continue
OL,16,Fto run all days of the week.           
OL,18,FIt came as Royal Mail reported a #219m 
OL,19,Funderlying operating loss for the six  
OL,20,Fmonths to 25 September.                
